        label(for="level") Politician's Level of Government:
        select(name="level" id="level" required) 
            option(value="") --Choose level of government--
            option(value="Local") Local
            option(value="State") State
            option(value="Federal") Federal
        br
        label(for="question") Question:
        select(name="question" id="question" required)  
            option(value="") --Choose question--
            option(value="question1") Should the mortgage interest deduction be eliminated from the tax code?
            option(value="question2") Should states relax scope of practice laws for nurse practitioners?
            option(value="question3") Should marijuana be legal?
            option(value="question4") Should gay marriage be legal?
            option(value="question5") Should defense spending be increased or decreased?
            option(value="question6") Should the US government support a coup in Venezuela?
